title: 'The Last Ship' Season 3 Spoilers: 'Jane the Virgin' Alum Bridget Regan Joins Cast, Plot Tackles Rebuilding America
text: 'The Last Ship' Season 3 Spoilers: 'Jane the Virgin' Alum Bridget Regan Joins Cast, Plot Tackles Rebuilding America Sunday, 25 October 2015 (16 minutes ago) The third season of the post-apocalyptic drama "The Last Ship" is still far away from its premiere day but updates coming in have revealed that there will be new faces that will be joining the show. First in the list of new casts is "Jane the Virgin" alum Bridget Regan. Aside from Regan, Fernando Chien ("Ray Donovan") and Dichen Lachman ("Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.") have been cast in recurring roles.
